data.description:
NEW ROOF !! A 15-minute commute to downtown Fort Worth. This charming home is nestled on a quiet cul de sac near a park and playground, it's the perfect spot for families in a friendly neighborhood. Updated foundation with warranty, recently serviced HVAC. Roof warranty in MLS media.
RARE 4TH BEDROOM OR POTENTIAL OFFICE SPACE ADJACENT TO THE MASTER BEDROOM.
Conveniently located with easy access to I-820 and I-35, your daily commute is a breeze. The highly-rated schools in Eagle Mountain ISD ensure top-notch education for your children. Featuring 4 bedrooms and an open floor plan, there's plenty of space for your family to grow. The updated interior paint adds a fresh, modern touch. Don't miss out on this fantastic home – it's a true gem! ASSUMABLE VA LOAN AT 2.75% FOR VETERANS THAT ARE QUALIFIED
